<html>
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="keywords" content="Contact Improvisation, Contact Improv, Contact Dance Improvisation, Contact Jams, Improv Dance Workshops Festivals">
    <meta http-equiv="expires" content="+3">
    <title>Contact Improvisation</title>
    <link href="contact.css" type="text/css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>
	<div class="main">
		<div class="content">

			<div class="banner_image">
				<a href="/"><img src="/images/ContactImprovNet-Banner.png" height="130" width="840" alt="" /></a>
			</div>

			<div class="navigation_bar">
				<table>
		    		<tr>
						<th class="navigation_bar_entry"><a href="/#Events">Workshops and Events</a></th>
						<th class="navigation_bar_entry"><a href="/jams.html">Jams and Classes</a></th>
						<th class="navigation_bar_entry"><a href="/people.html">People and Places</a></th>
			    	</tr>
		  		</table>
			</div>

			<div class="announcement">
				<fieldset>
					<legend>
						January 15, 2009 &mdash; Upgrading ContactImprov.net
					</legend>
					<p>
						We are working on making it easier for the Contact Improv community to 
						add information about <b>jams, workshops, classes and teachers</b> to this site
						and to keep that information up to date.

						We will be making a number of improvements to the site between now and mid-February -
						but we will never charge for any of our services.
				
						This site is a labor of love for the community, not a business.
					</p>
					<p>
						If you previously submitted an Event listing, we ask that you please <b>resubmit</b>
						the Event information by following these steps:
						<ol>
							<li>
								Fill out the 
								<a href="/user/request_account">Account Request form</a>
							</li>
							<li>
								Wait 0-48 hours for your request to be approved
							</li>
							<li>
								Once your account has been created, 
								<a href="/user">log in to your account</a>
							</li>
							<li>
								You will now be able to 
								<a href="/event/new">create Event listings</a> 
								or update your existing Event listings
							</li>
						</ol>
				
					</p>
				</fieldset>
			</div>

		  <p>If you are wondering what Contact Improv is, <a href="about.html">please click here</a>.</p>

		  <p>The site is organized into the following sections:</p>

		  <ul>
				<li><a href="#events">Events and Workshops</a>, listed chronologically. These are events that take place just once.
				<li><a href="jams.html">Ongoing Jams and Classes</a>
				<li><a href="people.html">People</a> and <a href="people.html#places">Places</a> teaching, performing, or otherwise involved in Contact
				<li><a href="announce.html">Announcements and Links</a> (notices, advertisements, etc.)
				<li><a href="photos/">Photographs</a> of Contact.
				<li><a href="ci25/ci25.html">CI25</a> was the celebration of the 25th Anniversary of Contact Improvisation, held at Oberlin College, June 1997. This section includes historical information about Contact including a bibliography and list of videos), so it might be useful to students of Contact. It also includes pointers to other celebrations of Contact held worldwide.
				<li><a href="writings.html">Essays, Articles, and Theses about Contact Improv</a> 
			</ul>

			<h2><a name="events" id="events">Workshops, Festivals, and Other Events</a></h2>

			<p>Events are listed in chronological order. For historical interest, see also the <a href="past-events.html">list of past events</a>.</p>

			<% @events.each do |event| %>
				<div style="clear: both; margin-bottom: 1.5em;">
					<div style="float: left; width: 12%;">
						<div class="date_box"> 
							<span class="day"><%= event.start_date.strftime('%e') %></span> 
							<span class="month"><%= event.start_date.strftime('%b').upcase %></span> 
						    <span class="year"><%= event.start_date.strftime('%Y') %></span> 
						</div>
						<% if event.start_date != event.end_date %>
							<div style="padding-left: 28px; padding-bottom: 4px;">
								to
							</div>
							<div class="date_box"> 
								<span class="day"><%= event.end_date.strftime('%e') %></span> 
								<span class="month"><%= event.end_date.strftime('%b') %></span> 
							    <span class="year"><%= event.end_date.strftime('%Y') %></span> 
							</div>
						<% end %>
					</div>
					<div style="float: right; width: 88%;">
						<div class='event'>
							<% if event.url %>
								<%= "<a href=\"#{event.url.address}\">#{event.title}</a>" %>
							<% else %>
								<%= event.title %>
							<% end %>
						</div>
						<div class='location'><%= format_entry_location(event) %></div>
						<div style="margin-left: 1em;">
							<div class='entry_description'>
								<%= RedCloth.new(event.description.strip, [:filter_html]).to_html %>
							</div>
							<% if !event.cost.blank? %>
								<div class='fee'>
									<%= RedCloth.new(event.cost.strip, [:filter_html]).to_html %>
								</div>
							<% end %>
							<div class='contact'><span style="color: #555;">CONTACT:</span> <%= format_contact_info(event) %></div>
							<div class='updated'>[<%= event.updated_at.strftime('%b %d %Y') %>]</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div style="clear: both; padding-top: 1.8em;"></div>
			<% end %>
			
			<p style="border-bottom: solid 1px black;" />

			<div style="font-size: small; text-align: right;">
				<p>
					As of January 15, 2009, this site is maintained by 
					<a href="http://craigharman.net">Craig Harman</a>,
					<br />
					with assistance from
					<a href="http://myriadicity.com/Sundry/FrontPage">Ken Manheimer</a>.
				</p>
				<p>
			        Many thanks to Jim Davis, Chris Deephouse and Mugsy Lunsford  
					<br />
					for maintaining and hosting this site for our benefit for many years.
				</p>
			</div>

		</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
